import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.hist(data['duration'])
    plt.xlabel('Flight Duration')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight durations?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    avg_delay_by_airline = data.groupby('airline')['delay_time'].mean()
    avg_delay_by_airline.plot(kind='bar')
    
    plt.xlabel('Airline')
    plt.ylabel('Average Delay Time')
    plt.title('What is the average delay time for flights?', wrap=True)
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    plt.scatter(data['departure_delay'], data['arrival_delay'])
    plt.xlabel('Departure Delay')
    plt.ylabel('Arrival Delay')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between departure delay and arrival delay?')
    
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):

    plt.hist(data['distance'], bins=20)

    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight distances?')

    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    
    cancellation_reasons = data['cancellation_reason'].value_counts()
    cancellation_reasons.plot(kind='bar')
    
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        plt.gca().xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    
    plt.title("What is the most common reason for flight cancellations?", wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
chart.show()
